[package]
authors = [ "nathanielsimard <nathaniel.simard.42@gmail.com>",]
categories = [ "science", "no-std", "embedded", "wasm",]
description = "Flexible and Comprehensive Deep Learning Framework in Rust"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/burn"
edition = "2021"
keywords = [ "deep-learning", "machine-learning", "tensor", "pytorch", "ndarray",]
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
name = "burn"
readme = "README.md"
repository = "https://github.com/tracel-ai/burn"
rust-version = "1.82"
version = "0.17.0"

[features]
default = [ "burn-core/default", "burn-train?/default", "std",]
doc = [ "default", "train", "burn-core/doc", "burn-train/doc",]
std = [ "burn-core/std",]
train = [ "burn-train", "autodiff", "dataset",]
tui = [ "burn-train?/tui",]
metrics = [ "burn-train?/sys-metrics",]
dataset = [ "burn-core/dataset",]
sqlite = [ "burn-core/sqlite",]
sqlite-bundled = [ "burn-core/sqlite-bundled",]
audio = [ "burn-core/audio",]
vision = [ "burn-core/vision",]
autodiff = [ "burn-core/autodiff",]
fusion = [ "burn-core/fusion",]
accelerate = [ "burn-core/accelerate",]
autotune = [ "burn-core/autotune",]
blas-netlib = [ "burn-core/blas-netlib",]
candle-cuda = [ "burn-core/candle-cuda",]
metal = [ "burn-core/metal",]
openblas = [ "burn-core/openblas",]
openblas-system = [ "burn-core/openblas-system",]
template = [ "burn-core/template",]
candle = [ "burn-core/candle",]
cuda = [ "burn-core/cuda",]
hip = [ "burn-core/hip",]
ndarray = [ "burn-core/ndarray",]
remote = [ "burn-core/remote",]
router = [ "burn-core/router",]
server = [ "burn-core/server",]
tch = [ "burn-core/tch",]
wgpu = [ "burn-core/wgpu",]
vulkan = [ "burn-core/vulkan",]
webgpu = [ "burn-core/webgpu",]
network = [ "burn-core/network",]
experimental-named-tensor = [ "burn-core/experimental-named-tensor",]
record-item-custom-serde = [ "burn-core/record-item-custom-serde",]

[dependencies.burn-core]
path = "../burn-core"
version = "0.17.0"
default-features = false

[dependencies.burn-train]
path = "../burn-train"
version = "0.17.0"
optional = true
default-features = false

[package]
authors = [ "nathanielsimard <nathaniel.simard.42@gmail.com>",]
categories = [ "science",]
description = "Automatic differentiation backend for the Burn framework"
edition = "2021"
keywords = [ "deep-learning", "machine-learning", "data",]
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
name = "burn-autodiff"
readme = "README.md"
repository = "https://github.com/tracel-ai/burn/tree/main/crates/burn-autodiff"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/burn-autodiff"
version = "0.17.0"

[features]
default = [ "std",]
export_tests = [ "burn-tensor-testgen",]
std = []
async = []

[dependencies.burn-common]
path = "../burn-common"
version = "0.17.0"
default-features = false

[dependencies.burn-tensor]
path = "../burn-tensor"
version = "0.17.0"
default-features = false

[dependencies.burn-tensor-testgen]
path = "../burn-tensor-testgen"
version = "0.17.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.derive-new]
version = "0.7.0"
default-features = false

[dependencies.spin]
version = "0.9.8"
features = [ "mutex", "spin_mutex", "portable-atomic",]

[dependencies.log]
default-features = false
version = "0.4.25"

[dev-dependencies.burn-tensor]
path = "../burn-tensor"
version = "0.17.0"
default-features = false
features = [ "export_tests",]

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
features = [ "default",]
rustdoc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]

[package]
authors = [ "louisfd <louisfd94@gmail.com>",]
categories = [ "science",]
description = "Candle backend for the Burn framework"
edition = "2021"
keywords = [ "deep-learning", "machine-learning", "data",]
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
name = "burn-candle"
readme = "README.md"
repository = "https://github.com/tracel-ai/burn/tree/main/crates/burn-candle"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/burn-candle"
version = "0.17.0"

[features]
default = [ "std",]
std = []
doc = [ "default",]
cuda = [ "candle-core/cuda",]
metal = [ "candle-core/metal",]
accelerate = [ "candle-core/accelerate",]

[dependencies.derive-new]
version = "0.7.0"
default-features = false

[dependencies.burn-tensor]
path = "../burn-tensor"
version = "0.17.0"
default-features = false

[dependencies.half]
version = "2.4.1"
features = [ "alloc", "num-traits", "serde",]
default-features = false

[dependencies.candle-core]
version = "0.8"

[dev-dependencies.burn-autodiff]
path = "../burn-autodiff"
version = "0.17.0"
default-features = false
features = [ "export_tests",]

[dev-dependencies.burn-tch]
path = "../burn-tch"
version = "0.17.0"
default-features = false
features = []

[dev-dependencies.burn-tensor]
path = "../burn-tensor"
version = "0.17.0"
default-features = false
features = [ "export_tests",]

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
features = [ "doc",]
rustdoc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]

[package]
authors = [ "Dilshod Tadjibaev (@antimora)",]
categories = []
description = "Common crate for the Burn framework"
edition = "2021"
keywords = []
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
name = "burn-common"
readme = "README.md"
repository = "https://github.com/tracel-ai/burn/tree/main/crates/burn-common"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/burn-common"
version = "0.17.0"

[features]
default = [ "std", "cubecl-common/default",]
std = [ "cubecl-common/std",]
doc = [ "default",]
network = [ "dep:indicatif", "dep:reqwest", "dep:tokio",]
rayon = [ "dep:rayon",]

[dev-dependencies]
dashmap = "6.1.0"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.217"
default-features = false
features = [ "derive", "alloc",]

[dependencies.indicatif]
optional = true
version = "0.17.9"

[dependencies.reqwest]
optional = true
version = "0.12.12"

[dependencies.tokio]
optional = true
version = "1.42.0"
features = [ "rt", "macros",]

[dependencies.rayon]
optional = true
version = "1.10.0"

[dependencies.cubecl-common]
default-features = false
git = "https://github.com/tracel-ai/cubecl"
rev = "ff34667accfe077d4a1cd48ae419868e142acfd6"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
features = [ "doc",]
rustdoc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]

[target."cfg(target_family = \"wasm\")".dependencies.getrandom]
features = [ "js",]
version = "0.2.15"
default-features = false

[target."cfg(target_family = \"wasm\")".dependencies.web-time]
version = "1.1.0"

[package]
authors = [ "nathanielsimard <nathaniel.simard.42@gmail.com>",]
categories = [ "science", "no-std", "embedded", "wasm",]
description = "Flexible and Comprehensive Deep Learning Framework in Rust"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/burn-core"
edition = "2021"
keywords = [ "deep-learning", "machine-learning", "tensor", "pytorch", "ndarray",]

name = "burn-core"

repository = "https://github.com/tracel-ai/burn/tree/main/crates/burn-core"
version = "0.17.0"

[features]
dataset = [ "burn-dataset",]
default = [ "std", "burn-candle?/default", "burn-common/default", "burn-dataset?/default", "burn-ndarray?/default", "burn-tch?/default", "burn-tensor/default", "burn-wgpu?/default", "burn-router?/default", "burn-cuda?/default", "burn-autodiff?/default", "burn-hip?/default",]
doc = [ "std", "dataset", "candle", "fusion", "ndarray", "tch", "wgpu", "cuda", "hip", "audio", "vision", "autodiff", "remote", "router", "server", "burn-candle/doc", "burn-common/doc", "burn-dataset/doc", "burn-ndarray/doc", "burn-tch/doc", "burn-tensor/doc", "burn-wgpu/doc", "burn-router/doc", "burn-cuda/doc", "burn-hip/doc",]
network = [ "burn-common/network",]
sqlite = [ "burn-dataset?/sqlite",]
sqlite-bundled = [ "burn-dataset?/sqlite-bundled",]
std = [ "burn-autodiff?/std", "bincode/std", "burn-candle?/std", "burn-common/std", "burn-ndarray?/std", "burn-tensor/std", "burn-wgpu?/std", "burn-router?/std", "burn-cuda?/std", "burn-hip?/std", "flate2", "half/std", "log", "rand/std", "rmp-serde", "serde/std", "serde_json/std", "num-traits/std",]
vision = [ "burn-dataset?/vision", "burn-common/network",]
audio = [ "burn-dataset?/audio",]
autodiff = [ "burn-autodiff",]
fusion = [ "burn-wgpu?/fusion", "burn-cuda?/fusion",]
accelerate = [ "burn-candle?/accelerate", "burn-ndarray?/blas-accelerate",]
autotune = [ "burn-wgpu?/autotune", "burn-cuda?/autotune", "burn-hip?/autotune",]
blas-netlib = [ "burn-ndarray?/blas-netlib",]
metal = [ "burn-candle?/metal",]
openblas = [ "burn-ndarray?/blas-openblas",]
openblas-system = [ "burn-ndarray?/blas-openblas-system",]
remote = [ "burn-remote/client",]
router = [ "burn-router",]
server = [ "burn-remote/server",]
template = [ "burn-wgpu?/template",]
candle = [ "burn-candle",]
candle-cuda = [ "candle", "burn-candle/cuda",]
cuda = [ "burn-cuda",]
hip = [ "burn-hip",]
ndarray = [ "burn-ndarray",]
tch = [ "burn-tch",]
wgpu = [ "burn-wgpu",]
vulkan = [ "wgpu", "burn-wgpu/vulkan",]
webgpu = [ "wgpu", "burn-wgpu/webgpu",]
record-item-custom-serde = [ "thiserror", "regex",]
experimental-named-tensor = [ "burn-tensor/experimental-named-tensor",]
test-cuda = [ "cuda",]
test-hip = [ "hip",]
test-tch = [ "tch",]
test-wgpu = [ "wgpu",]
test-wgpu-spirv = [ "test-wgpu", "vulkan",]

[dev-dependencies]
tempfile = "3.14.0"

[dependencies.burn-common]

[package]
authors = [ "nathanielsimard <nathaniel.simard.42@gmail.com>",]
categories = [ "science",]
description = "Generic backend that can be compiled just-in-time to any shader language target"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/burn-jit"
edition = "2021"
keywords = [ "deep-learning", "machine-learning", "gpu",]
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
name = "burn-jit"
readme = "README.md"
repository = "https://github.com/tracel-ai/burn/tree/main/crates/burn-jit"
version = "0.17.0"

[features]
autotune = []
default = [ "autotune", "std", "fusion", "cubecl/default",]
doc = [ "default",]
export_tests = [ "burn-tensor-testgen", "serial_test", "burn-autodiff/export_tests", "burn-tensor/export_tests", "burn-ndarray", "fusion", "paste",]
fusion = [ "burn-fusion",]
fusion-experimental = [ "fusion",]
std = [ "cubecl/std", "burn-tensor/std",]
template = []

[dependencies]
bytemuck = "1.21.0"
hashbrown = "0.15.2"

[dependencies.burn-common]
path = "../burn-common"
version = "0.17.0"

[dependencies.burn-fusion]
path = "../burn-fusion"
version = "0.17.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.burn-tensor]
path = "../burn-tensor"
version = "0.17.0"
default-features = false
features = [ "cubecl", "repr",]

[dependencies.cubecl]
features = [ "linalg", "reduce",]
git = "https://github.com/tracel-ai/cubecl"
default-features = false
rev = "ff34667accfe077d4a1cd48ae419868e142acfd6"

[dependencies.derive-new]
version = "0.7.0"
default-features = false

[dependencies.half]
features = [ "bytemuck", "alloc", "num-traits", "serde",]
version = "2.4.1"
default-features = false

[dependencies.log]
default-features = false
version = "0.4.25"

[dependencies.num-traits]
version = "0.2.19"
default-features = false
features = [ "libm",]

[dependencies.rand]
version = "0.8.5"
default-features = false
features = [ "std_rng",]

[dependencies.spin]
version = "0.9.8"
features = [ "mutex", "spin_mutex", "portable-atomic",]

[dependencies.futures-lite]
features = [ "std",]
version = "2.5.0"
default-features = false

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.217"
default-features = false
features = [ "derive", "alloc",]

[dependencies.text_placeholder]
features = [ "struct_context",]
version = "0.5.1"

[dependencies.burn-tensor-testgen]
path = "../burn-tensor-testgen"
version = "0.17.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.burn-autodiff]
path = "../burn-autodiff"
version = "0.17.0"
default-features = false
optional = true

[dependencies.burn-ndarray]
path = "../burn-ndarray"
version = "0.17.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.paste]
optional = true
version = "1"

[dependencies.serial_test]
optional = true
version = "3.2.0"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
features = [ "doc",]
rustdoc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]
